    • testinteractObjectAtWithZeroCellSize

      @Test void testinteractObjectAtWithZeroCellSize()

    • testinteractObjectAtWithNegativeCellSize

      @Test void testinteractObjectAtWithNegativeCellSize()
      Tests the behavior of interactObjectAt when the game view returns a negative cell size. In this case, the controller should not be called.
